  MC-6800 interrupt vectors (top 8 bytes of ROM D, $FFF8-$FFFF):

  VECTOR ADDR     NAME    TARGET      FUNCTION
  ------------------------------------------------------------
  $FFF8 / $FFF9   IRQ     -> $ED83    Serial/printer ISR (ACIA1 + PRNTER)
  $FFFA / $FFFB   SWI     -> $E800    Cold boot fallback
  $FFFC / $FFFD   NMI     -> $E800    Cold boot fallback
  $FFFE / $FFFF   RST     -> $E800    Power-on RESET -> ROM B cold boot

